Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model

Class Square

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Square
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AmmoSquare, SpawnSquare
    public abstract class Square
extends java.lang.Object
    Is the abstract class of squares, which completely describes it as object of the map. Collection (in the sense of grabbing on it) is left to concrete extensions.
